flowchart TD
    A[User taps Join Random Game] --> B[JoinRandomGameWidget]
    B --> C[checkCoinsRequirement]
    C --> D[ensureWebSocketReady]
    D --> E[Set isRandomJoinInProgress]
    E --> F[Emit join_random_game]
    F --> G[Backend find or create room]
    G --> H{New room created}
    H -->|Yes| I[room_creation success is_random_join]
    I --> J[Update state clear flag]
    J --> K[Delay 300ms]
    K --> L[Navigate to game-play]
    H -->|No| M[Join existing room]
    M --> N[websocket_join_room hook]
    N --> O[Set currentGameId currentRoomId]
    O --> P[Wait for game_state_updated]
    P --> Q[handleGameStateUpdated adds game to map]
    Q --> R[Game in Current games list]
    R --> S[User taps game]
    S --> T[setCurrentGameSync]
    T --> L
